1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:15,000
=Episode 7=

3
00:00:18,760 --> 00:00:20,120
Chu Yunchang, you're under arrest.

4
00:00:21,559 --> 00:00:22,120
Father?

5
00:00:22,239 --> 00:00:24,120
Wait, what is the meaning of this?

6
00:00:24,559 --> 00:00:25,199
Buyu.

7
00:00:25,480 --> 00:00:28,239
She is the Jade Squirrel,
Sect Leader of the Sacred Hand Sect.

8
00:00:32,679 --> 00:00:33,640
What proof do you have?

9
00:00:33,799 --> 00:00:35,240
Lady Thousand-Hands, Lin Xin'er,

10
00:00:35,240 --> 00:00:37,079
identified her personally from prison.

11
00:00:37,719 --> 00:00:39,759
I don't even know a Lin Xin'er.

12
00:00:40,079 --> 00:00:40,719
Buyu.

13
00:00:41,359 --> 00:00:43,039
I can vouch for this myself.

14
00:00:43,679 --> 00:00:45,119
Lin Xin'er named her.

15
00:00:45,479 --> 00:00:46,200
It's her.

16
00:00:50,079 --> 00:00:50,759
Buyu.

17
00:00:52,359 --> 00:00:54,079
Are you trying to protect Chu Yunchang?

18
00:00:54,800 --> 00:00:55,519
Wushuang.

19
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:58,290
Did you actually
see the Jade Squirrel last night?

20
00:00:58,679 --> 00:01:00,560
Are you absolutely sure it was Yunchang?

21
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,479
What are you implying?

22
00:01:05,719 --> 00:01:07,200
Chang was injured saving my sister

23
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:08,519
and hasn't recovered yet.

24
00:01:08,920 --> 00:01:10,760
Her wounds reopened today.
She nearly died.

25
00:01:12,920 --> 00:01:13,840
My sister also said

26
00:01:14,359 --> 00:01:16,159
that Chang was right here all night.

27
00:01:16,159 --> 00:01:17,359
She didn't leave for a second.

28
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:19,000
If you really saw

29
00:01:19,000 --> 00:01:20,239
the Jade Squirrel last night,

30
00:01:20,480 --> 00:01:21,799
then it couldn't have been Chang.

31
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:25,760
Whether it was her or not,

32
00:01:26,439 --> 00:01:28,120
we need to take her in for questioning.

33
00:01:30,840 --> 00:01:31,519
Buyu.

34
00:01:32,187 --> 00:01:33,746
Wushuang is just doing her job.

35
00:01:34,200 --> 00:01:34,761
Take her.

36
00:01:40,879 --> 00:01:41,519
Buyu...

37
00:01:42,959 --> 00:01:44,120
It's okay. I'll go with them.

38
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:48,400
Buyu,

39
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:49,680
you can't visit her in prison.

40
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:50,640
Stay out of this!

41
00:01:50,719 --> 00:01:51,760
Chang is only a suspect,

42
00:01:51,760 --> 00:01:52,519
not a criminal.

43
00:01:52,519 --> 00:01:53,400
Why should I recuse myself?

44
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:53,760
You...

45
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:55,519
Everyone knows about your relationship.

46
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:56,719
You have to recuse yourself.

47
00:01:57,439 --> 00:01:58,000
Rong,

48
00:01:58,159 --> 00:01:59,040
perfect timing.

49
00:01:59,110 --> 00:02:00,480
You were watching Chang that night.

50
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:02,000
There's no way
she could have gone out.

51
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,040
I'm sorry, Buyu.

52
00:02:03,519 --> 00:02:05,319
I was in Yunchang's room

53
00:02:05,319 --> 00:02:06,280
the entire night,

54
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,000
but I did fall asleep for a while.

55
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,439
I can't rule out the possibility

56
00:02:09,439 --> 00:02:10,719
that she's the Jade Squirrel.

57
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:12,280
Well said, Rong.

58
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:17,280
Last night, I told Rong
to look after Chu Yunchang,

59
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:19,199
but that was actually
a cover to monitor her.

60
00:02:19,439 --> 00:02:22,000
Instead,
Rong slept like a log the entire night.

61
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:24,080
Just like that time
in the Three-Hand Sect dungeon,

62
00:02:24,080 --> 00:02:26,599
she completely missed it
when Chu Yunchang moved against Li Wan.

63
00:02:26,879 --> 00:02:29,120
Then, we had a run-in
with the Jade Squirrel

64
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,199
and managed to wound her.

65
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:33,000
Now, Chu Yunchang's old injury
just happens to flare up.

66
00:02:33,439 --> 00:02:36,039
Do you really believe
this is all just a coincidence?

67
00:02:36,039 --> 00:02:37,500
Do you have a solid chain of evidence?

68
00:02:37,700 --> 00:02:39,479
Is Lin Xin'er's testimony
not enough for you?

69
00:02:41,439 --> 00:02:42,680
I will find the proof I need

70
00:02:43,159 --> 00:02:44,890
to show that Chang
isn't the Jade Squirrel.

71
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,560
And when I do, all of you

72
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,800
will owe her a formal apology.

73
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:48,800
(Honorable and incorruptible)
Mao Buyu!

74
00:02:49,280 --> 00:02:51,199
You have completely lost your mind!

75
00:02:53,187 --> 00:02:57,725
(Gate Bureau, Ministry of Justice)

76
00:02:57,812 --> 00:03:01,200
(Ministry of Justice)

77
00:03:05,050 --> 00:03:06,490
(Ministry of Justice)
So, this is the Gate Bureau.

78
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:09,120
It's certainly impressive.

79
00:03:09,479 --> 00:03:10,960
Fitting for a man of my status.

80
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:14,450
(Ministry of Justice)

81
00:03:15,210 --> 00:03:16,240
This is a restricted area.

82
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:17,120
No unauthorized entry.

83
00:03:17,400 --> 00:03:18,439
Unauthorized?

84
00:03:18,439 --> 00:03:19,560
Look closely, pal.

85
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:22,240
I'm the future of this entire Bureau.

86
00:03:23,080 --> 00:03:24,790
I don't care
if you're the sun god himself.

87
00:03:25,439 --> 00:03:26,000
Why, you...

88
00:03:28,639 --> 00:03:29,199
Hey, brother.

89
00:03:29,199 --> 00:03:30,590
You're with the Gate Bureau, right?

90
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,560
We're all brothers here.

91
00:03:32,759 --> 00:03:33,360
Here.

92
00:03:33,700 --> 00:03:35,039
Take the boys out for some drinks.

93
00:03:36,439 --> 00:03:37,560
What, not enough?

94
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:38,560
Wait, there's more.

95
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:41,280
Take it all.

96
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,360
Arrest him.

97
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:45,439
You!

98
00:03:45,439 --> 00:03:46,400
What is this?

99
00:03:46,920 --> 00:03:48,240
Trespassing on Gate Bureau grounds

100
00:03:48,240 --> 00:03:49,680
and attempting to bribe a Constable.

101
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,919
Your action is highly suspicious.

102
00:03:50,919 --> 00:03:51,319
Bribe?

103
00:03:51,319 --> 00:03:52,159
This is the evidence.

104
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,560
Seize and interrogate him.

105
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,319
Yes, Constable Mao.

106
00:03:54,319 --> 00:03:55,800
Do you have any idea who I am?

107
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,159
Move it.

108
00:03:56,159 --> 00:03:57,039
Nice one, kid.

109
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,520
I'm going to remember your face.

110
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,479
(Gate Bureau, Ministry of Justice)
I am the Young Master...

111
00:04:00,039 --> 00:04:00,879
Ouch, go each on me.

112
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,560
Buyu.

113
00:04:05,039 --> 00:04:05,800
Squire Mei.

114
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,000
Your tea, sir.

115
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:14,039
You know as well as I do
that Chang is weak and helpless.

116
00:04:14,439 --> 00:04:16,959
How could she possibly
be the Jade Squirrel?

117
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:19,199
Unless, of course,

118
00:04:19,199 --> 00:04:21,240
we can prove the Queen Thief
of the South was lying.

119
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:25,519
That's the hard part.

120
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:27,519
Lin Xin'er has been caught.

121
00:04:27,519 --> 00:04:29,839
She's naturally
taking down Chang with her.

122
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,399
Why do you say that?

123
00:04:32,160 --> 00:04:33,000
Well, years ago,

124
00:04:33,000 --> 00:04:33,959
(Xiangming Tea House)
our family had

125
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:35,199
business dealings with the Lins.

126
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,720
Everything seemed
perfectly fine at first,

127
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,839
but then we slowly realized

128
00:04:40,439 --> 00:04:42,439
that they were actually
a family of thieves.

129
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,839
So, my father-in-law

130
00:04:45,399 --> 00:04:47,240
reported them to the authorities.

131
00:04:48,399 --> 00:04:50,360
Elder Chu was
perfectly justified in doing so.

132
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,120
That may be true, but...

133
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:54,160
But because of that,

134
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,639
he made an enemy of the Lin family.

135
00:04:57,890 --> 00:04:58,800
If we could only prove

136
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,690
that Lin Xin'er is
framing Chang out of spite...

137
00:05:01,439 --> 00:05:03,160
But unfortunately, there is no evidence.

138
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,120
Thanks for the insight.

139
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:12,480
As for the evidence,

140
00:05:12,839 --> 00:05:13,839
I'll find a way.

141
00:05:14,879 --> 00:05:16,439
I'm counting on you, Buyu.

142
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:45,519
Chang.

143
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:51,199
I'm not supposed to come here.

144
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:53,079
But, I had to sneak in tonight.

145
00:05:54,079 --> 00:05:54,639
Quick.

146
00:05:56,879 --> 00:05:57,480
Chang.

147
00:05:57,580 --> 00:05:58,759
This place is cold and damp.

148
00:05:58,759 --> 00:05:59,600
It's bad for recovery.

149
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:01,439
So I brought you an extra blanket.

150
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:02,959
Here.

151
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:06,360
Try this.

152
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:09,839
I'm fine, don't worry about me.

153
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:11,079
Sit.

154
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:16,759
I just don't understand

155
00:06:17,199 --> 00:06:18,160
why Lin Xin'er

156
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:20,480
is going to such lengths to frame me.

157
00:06:21,519 --> 00:06:22,639
It seems her ancestors

158
00:06:23,079 --> 00:06:24,639
had a feud with your grandfather.

159
00:06:26,120 --> 00:06:28,399
Don't worry. I'll keep digging.

160
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:33,839
Buyu.

161
00:06:34,399 --> 00:06:35,720
You have to believe me.

162
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,639
I have never done anything

163
00:06:37,639 --> 00:06:39,000
to harm an innocent soul.

164
00:06:39,519 --> 00:06:40,360
I believe you.

165
00:06:40,839 --> 00:06:42,000
Just focus on getting better.

166
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:44,879
Leave the rest to me.

167
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,079
It's just that...

168
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:53,000
there's one thing
I can't wrap my head around.

169
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:55,079
Why would Lin Xin'er name you

170
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:57,720
out of all people?

171
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:01,580
If this is just a personal vendetta,

172
00:07:02,160 --> 00:07:03,519
she has to know

173
00:07:03,879 --> 00:07:06,079
how easy it would be
to disprove a false accusation.

174
00:07:07,639 --> 00:07:09,079
She can't be that silly.

175
00:07:10,900 --> 00:07:11,981
How should I know?

176
00:07:12,437 --> 00:07:13,517
Maybe...

177
00:07:15,240 --> 00:07:16,800
Maybe she's just out of her mind.

178
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:21,879
Chang.

179
00:07:22,879 --> 00:07:24,319
Do you know the Jade Squirrel?

180
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:27,360
Why would you ask me that?

181
00:07:30,079 --> 00:07:31,879
I obviously don't believe you are her.

182
00:07:33,319 --> 00:07:35,480
But if you, or your family,

183
00:07:35,480 --> 00:07:37,040
were ever indebted to her,

184
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:38,959
and out of loyalty

185
00:07:39,720 --> 00:07:41,720
you're covering for her...

186
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:45,240
Please, just tell me the truth.

187
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,319
Nothing of the sort.

188
00:07:47,560 --> 00:07:51,120
My family has absolutely no connection

189
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,839
to the underworld.

190
00:07:54,725 --> 00:07:56,759
Whether the Jade Squirrel is a hero

191
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,959
or a common criminal,

192
00:07:58,399 --> 00:07:59,160
before the law,

193
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:00,800
there is no room for personal sentiment.

194
00:08:01,639 --> 00:08:02,360
Chang,

195
00:08:02,839 --> 00:08:03,879
you must tell me if you are

196
00:08:03,879 --> 00:08:04,879
in a difficult position.

197
00:08:05,319 --> 00:08:07,160
I will protect you, no matter what.

198
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:12,525
What if...

199
00:08:13,879 --> 00:08:15,720
Hypothetically speaking, of course.

200
00:08:16,759 --> 00:08:18,839
What if I really were the Jade Squirrel?

201
00:08:20,639 --> 00:08:22,040
What would you do then?

202
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:32,919
I think...

203
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:36,559
you must have had your reasons.

204
00:08:37,975 --> 00:08:39,014
Would you arrest me?

205
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:40,320
Yes.

206
00:08:41,240 --> 00:08:42,440
Because I'm a constable.

207
00:08:43,710 --> 00:08:45,879
But I would do
everything in my power to find evidence

208
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,440
to help reduce your sentence.

209
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:52,120
And would you still want to marry me?

210
00:08:52,559 --> 00:08:53,159
I would.

211
00:08:54,559 --> 00:08:55,679
No matter how long it takes,

212
00:08:56,279 --> 00:08:57,279
I'd wait for you.

213
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:04,440
And what if I were sentenced to death?

214
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:10,320
Don't talk like that.

215
00:09:12,799 --> 00:09:13,900
Trying to get away with it?

216
00:09:14,519 --> 00:09:15,240
Keep dreaming.

217
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,440
Rest well.

218
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,919
I'll visit you again.

219
00:09:24,039 --> 00:09:25,039
Come before nightfall.

220
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:28,080
It's so dark in here.

221
00:09:28,200 --> 00:09:29,080
I'm scared.

222
00:09:35,759 --> 00:09:36,559
Wait here.

223
00:09:39,725 --> 00:09:43,837
♪Donning a mask to hide my heart♪

224
00:09:43,912 --> 00:09:47,462
♪Playing a part with a hollow smile♪

225
00:09:47,875 --> 00:09:51,575
♪Pitted against each other,
neither of us gives in♪

226
00:09:51,875 --> 00:09:55,700
♪One is cold as ice,
the other is burning like fire♪

227
00:09:55,900 --> 00:09:59,662
♪A love so deep,
yet destiny so fleeting♪

228
00:09:59,862 --> 00:10:03,650
♪This fervor is buried deep within♪

229
00:10:03,787 --> 00:10:07,575
♪I long for it so much,
I crave to return♪

230
00:10:07,900 --> 00:10:11,400
♪To the moment we first met♪

231
00:10:11,537 --> 00:10:16,125
♪Casting aside all obsession
just to be with you♪

232
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:16,879
Well?

233
00:10:17,500 --> 00:10:18,360
It's not as dark now.

234
00:10:19,800 --> 00:10:21,512
♪I can't untie the knot in your heart♪

235
00:10:21,559 --> 00:10:23,799
Tonight, I'll borrow some light
from the moon

236
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:25,159
with this basin.

237
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,799
Don't worry.

238
00:10:28,159 --> 00:10:29,440
I'll keep searching for evidence

239
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:30,720
to earn your freedom.

240
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:35,775
♪But I'll spend my life
keeping you safe♪

241
00:10:35,850 --> 00:10:39,600
♪Lies and vows,
let them stay in the past♪

242
00:10:39,837 --> 00:10:41,812
♪Let's return to when we first met♪

243
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:43,120
Tonight...

244
00:10:44,860 --> 00:10:45,720
is a beautiful night.

245
00:11:33,759 --> 00:11:34,799
You...

246
00:11:40,039 --> 00:11:41,879
You...

247
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:46,039
Help! Guards!

248
00:11:46,360 --> 00:11:47,200
Is anyone there?

249
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,120
(Jailer, Jin Dian)
What's with the yelling?

250
00:11:48,380 --> 00:11:49,559
It's the middle of the night!

251
00:11:49,639 --> 00:11:50,559
Someone is here.

252
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:51,840
Right here!

253
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:55,639
There's no one.

254
00:11:56,159 --> 00:11:57,320
She was here a moment ago!

255
00:11:57,320 --> 00:11:58,879
She was right in this cell!

256
00:11:58,879 --> 00:12:00,600
Shut up or get whipped!

257
00:12:00,600 --> 00:12:01,120
But I...

258
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:26,960
Where is the Sacred Token?

259
00:12:27,559 --> 00:12:29,720
How did you get in here?

260
00:12:30,399 --> 00:12:31,879
Haven't you heard?

261
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:34,600
It's the Sacred Hand Sect's
Space-Shifting Arts.

262
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:36,720
What do you want?

263
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:41,137
If you don't want to talk,

264
00:12:41,440 --> 00:12:42,399
that's fine.

265
00:12:43,975 --> 00:12:47,159
But then I can't guarantee
this little vial

266
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:49,679
won't find its way into your eyes.

267
00:12:50,759 --> 00:12:51,360
You...

268
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:53,600
You!

269
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,960
Guards! Someone, help!

270
00:12:58,320 --> 00:13:00,240
Guards! Help me!

271
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,799
Someone's trying to kill me!

272
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:03,320
Have you lost your mind?

273
00:13:03,320 --> 00:13:04,120
No, no!

274
00:13:04,559 --> 00:13:05,399
It was her!

275
00:13:06,759 --> 00:13:07,519
Who?

276
00:13:11,799 --> 00:13:13,240
Her! It was her!

277
00:13:13,240 --> 00:13:14,320
She just tried to kill me!

278
00:13:14,670 --> 00:13:15,750
She was going to kill me!

279
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:16,461
It was her!

280
00:13:21,279 --> 00:13:21,879
Get up.

281
00:13:26,340 --> 00:13:27,360
What were you just doing?

282
00:13:27,960 --> 00:13:28,600
Sleeping.

283
00:13:34,761 --> 00:13:35,362
Crazy woman.

284
00:13:35,362 --> 00:13:37,041
You're nothing but lies and nonsense!

285
00:13:38,279 --> 00:13:39,480
No! Don't go!

286
00:13:39,690 --> 00:13:40,799
I need to see Constable Mao!

287
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:41,679
Constable Mao!

288
00:13:41,987 --> 00:13:42,823
Constable Mao!

289
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:44,750
I have to see Constable Mao!

290
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:46,080
I need to see him!

291
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:47,120
Help!

292
00:13:47,879 --> 00:13:48,559
Constable Mao!

293
00:13:48,559 --> 00:13:49,519
You're finally here!

294
00:13:51,039 --> 00:13:51,610
Constable Mao!

295
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:52,440
Come here!

296
00:13:52,500 --> 00:13:53,080
Constable Mao!

297
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:54,879
Listen to me!

298
00:13:55,240 --> 00:13:56,480
Chu Yunchang

299
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,960
used the Space-Shifting Arts

300
00:13:57,960 --> 00:13:59,679
to suddenly appear right here!

301
00:13:59,700 --> 00:14:00,960
She was there, then she was over here!

302
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:02,080
Then, she talked to me.

303
00:14:02,080 --> 00:14:02,759
She was threatening me!

304
00:14:02,759 --> 00:14:04,120
She's going to kill me!

305
00:14:04,120 --> 00:14:07,240
She had this little vial in her hand,
some kind of heart-piercing poison!

306
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,559
The moment I closed my eyes,

307
00:14:08,559 --> 00:14:09,720
she tried to drop it in!

308
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:10,559
She wants me dead.

309
00:14:10,559 --> 00:14:11,200
- She means it!
- Alright, alright.

310
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:12,559
I get it. Calm down.

311
00:14:14,679 --> 00:14:15,279
Jin Dian.

312
00:14:16,360 --> 00:14:17,000
Check her.

313
00:14:17,279 --> 00:14:17,879
Yes.

314
00:14:20,279 --> 00:14:22,600
She used the Space-Shifting Arts
to try and kill me!

315
00:14:22,919 --> 00:14:25,240
She's really trying to kill me,
Constable Mao!

316
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,399
You have to believe me!

317
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:27,519
Please, believe me!

318
00:14:28,279 --> 00:14:28,840
We checked it.

319
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,540
- It's just ordinary wound medicine.
- Right, right.

320
00:14:30,559 --> 00:14:31,480
She's severely injured.

321
00:14:31,480 --> 00:14:33,039
So, she was permitted to keep a vial.

322
00:14:34,759 --> 00:14:35,720
This is the one!

323
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:37,890
She used this very vial
to poison my eyes and kill me!

324
00:14:39,310 --> 00:14:40,080
Give it back to her.

325
00:14:40,559 --> 00:14:41,360
No, Constable Mao!

326
00:14:41,360 --> 00:14:42,080
You have to believe me!

327
00:14:42,080 --> 00:14:42,720
Enough.

328
00:14:43,279 --> 00:14:44,000
Believe me!

329
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:45,380
- You have to believe me!
- Move aside.

330
00:14:49,279 --> 00:14:50,759
Don't lock it! Don't lock it!

331
00:14:51,440 --> 00:14:54,200
You hurt my Auntie.

332
00:14:54,519 --> 00:14:57,919
Do you really think
I'd let you off that easily?

333
00:14:58,440 --> 00:15:00,759
You hurt my Auntie.

334
00:15:01,330 --> 00:15:06,330
Do you really think
I'd let you off that easily?

335
00:15:29,550 --> 00:15:30,190
Yu?

336
00:15:31,520 --> 00:15:32,519
What are you doing here?

337
00:15:33,000 --> 00:15:34,690
I heard you were
interrogating Lin Xin'er.

338
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:35,800
I wanted to see for myself.

339
00:15:37,080 --> 00:15:39,120
This case involves Chu Yunchang.

340
00:15:39,130 --> 00:15:40,240
You should stay out of this.

341
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,080
Don't worry.

342
00:15:42,519 --> 00:15:44,320
I'm just here to observe,
not to interfere.

343
00:15:45,399 --> 00:15:46,919
I trust your capabilities, Wushuang.

344
00:15:46,919 --> 00:15:49,120
I know you won't let
an innocent person be harmed.

345
00:15:50,350 --> 00:15:51,230
Naturally.

346
00:15:52,480 --> 00:15:53,879
Since this concerns your fiancée,

347
00:15:54,262 --> 00:15:55,542
I will investigate it thoroughly.

348
00:15:58,759 --> 00:15:59,399
My Lady.

349
00:15:59,639 --> 00:16:01,240
Lin Xin'er seems to have lost her mind.

350
00:16:02,520 --> 00:16:04,320
She was perfectly fine
before she was caught.

351
00:16:04,320 --> 00:16:06,120
Why the sudden breakdown
after being jailed?

352
00:16:06,759 --> 00:16:08,759
If Lin Xin'er really is
mentally unstable,

353
00:16:09,360 --> 00:16:10,320
then her testimony

354
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:11,840
won't hold any weight, will it?

355
00:16:12,039 --> 00:16:13,679
Are you trying to shield Chu Yunchang?

356
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,000
How can I shield her

357
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:16,080
when there isn't a verdict?

358
00:16:16,240 --> 00:16:18,000
Don't forget that you're a constable.

359
00:16:18,000 --> 00:16:19,919
It's because I'm a constable

360
00:16:20,519 --> 00:16:21,360
that I refuse

361
00:16:21,360 --> 00:16:23,320
to let an innocent person be framed.

362
00:16:30,062 --> 00:16:33,337
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

363
00:16:33,375 --> 00:16:36,250
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

364
00:16:36,750 --> 00:16:42,468
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

365
00:16:43,650 --> 00:16:46,970
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

366
00:16:47,100 --> 00:16:50,020
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

367
00:16:51,188 --> 00:16:56,428
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

368
00:16:57,650 --> 00:17:00,043
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

369
00:17:00,043 --> 00:17:03,693
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

370
00:17:03,762 --> 00:17:07,252
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

371
00:17:07,350 --> 00:17:10,325
♪To the ends of time♪

372
00:17:10,325 --> 00:17:13,700
♪The moon traces your face♪

373
00:17:13,887 --> 00:17:17,475
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

374
00:17:17,475 --> 00:17:23,715
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

375
00:17:24,050 --> 00:17:27,265
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

376
00:17:27,550 --> 00:17:31,088
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

377
00:17:31,375 --> 00:17:34,400
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

378
00:17:34,400 --> 00:17:37,500
♪On our way to forever♪

379
00:17:37,500 --> 00:17:41,350
♪The moon traces your face♪

380
00:17:41,350 --> 00:17:44,710
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

381
00:17:44,900 --> 00:17:50,860
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

382
00:17:51,937 --> 00:18:01,577
♪Just to be with you♪

